From: sourcemod-css34 builder
Subject: [PATCH] CS:S v34 compatibility for SourceMod 1.11.0-git6572

Diff between upstream SourceMod at commit 832519ab647cdecb85763918dbfed1cb5e79c6cb
(v1.11.0-git6572) and the rom4s CSS34 build patches.

Normalize CRLF to LF in *.h, *.cpp, AMBuildScript, and tools/buildbot/Versioning
before applying (apply-sourcemod.sh does this automatically).

Apply from the sourcemod/ directory:
  patch -p1 < ../builder/patches/sourcemod-6572-css34.patch

--- a/AMBuildScript
+++ b/AMBuildScript
@@ -37,6 +37,7 @@
 
